<rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>some.pics (中文)</title><link>https://some.pics</link><description>只是网上的一些图片。</description><language>zh-CN</language><lastBuildDate>Fri, 15 May 2026 16:47:35 +0000</lastBuildDate><item><title/><link>https://some.pics/6a074e251788a</link><description>&lt;p&gt;今天的反思与不同的天空。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="A blue and cloudy sky in a puddle near a crossroad." height="2000" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/z428/6a074e251788a.jpg" width="1126"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://z428.some.pics"&gt;@z428&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 15 May 2026 16:47:35 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title>美国职业</title><link>https://some.pics/6a0741a1000ea</link><description>&lt;p&gt;美国专业&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="An advertising board, with a woman in tight sportswear working out. A man walks past smoking a cigarette. " height="4791" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/pigpog/6a0741a1000ea.jpg" width="7186"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://pigpog.some.pics"&gt;@pigpog&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 15 May 2026 15:54:13 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title>新雕塑两天进展</title><link>https://some.pics/6a073b8b5b3cc</link><description>&lt;p&gt;我昨天开始了一个新雕塑，两天下来就做到了这个程度。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="Green fussy textile sculpture on green background. Around the sculpture are some tools like yellow scissors, a crocheting needle and colorful markings." height="3023" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/lis/6a073b8b5b3cc.jpg" width="4031"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://lis.some.pics"&gt;@lis&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 15 May 2026 15:28:16 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title/><link>https://some.pics/6a072378a1085</link><description>&lt;p&gt;#FensterFreitag&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="Looking through a window covered in water drops. The background is blurred, but one can identify some hills on different shades of green and a very grey sky. The landscape is displayed upside-down in every droplet. " height="3000" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/roteskuffen/6a072378a1085.jpg" width="4000"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://roteskuffen.some.pics"&gt;@roteskuffen&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 15 May 2026 13:45:31 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title/><link>https://some.pics/6a070472d38c9</link><description>&lt;p&gt;我们花园里有一只狐狸，正抬头看着鸟食台——它在草地上吃了好一会儿东西。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="A fox in our garden, looking up at the bird table - spent a while eating something from the grass." height="1366" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/pigpog/6a070472d38c9.jpg" width="2048"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://pigpog.some.pics"&gt;@pigpog&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 15 May 2026 11:33:09 +0000</pubDate></item></channel></rss>